I bought the game for nostalgia, which is probably why I forgot how short it truly is. The game worked almost flawlessly, except the same glitches it always had at the end where Freddi is speaking, but Luther's mouth is moving. The only complaint I have, which I believe is shared by all, is that the app costs way too much. I would be more comfortable paying $1-2, but $5 is ridiculous. Unless they lower the price for the apps, then this will be the only game I buy.
